title: How To Milk a Cow
description:
Today I show you how to correctly milk a cow. Milking a cow can be an extremely dangerous task if you don't know how to do it correctly, so it's important that you learn from me; a trained professional milker (All animals, including grandparents) . How do you think farmers learnt to milk their cattle? I taught them. 

When it comes to milking cattle there are quite a few popular methods, such as:
1. Milking a Cow by Hand
2. Milking a Cow by Machine
3. Milking a Cow by Foot
4. Milking a Cow by Big Toe
5. Milking a Cow by Sloth
6. Milking a Cow by Erect Teat

All of which are covered and explained in this video.
